org.llrp.ltk.generated.parameters

Class AntennaConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.llrp.ltk.types.LLRPParameter
      • org.llrp.ltk.types.TLVParameter
        • org.llrp.ltk.generated.parameters.AntennaConfiguration

  • public class AntennaConfiguration
extends TLVParameter
    This parameter carries a single antenna's configuration and it specifies the default values for the parameter set that are passed in this parameter block. The scope of the default values is the antenna. The default values are used for parameters during an operation on this antenna if the parameter was unspecified in the spec that describes the operation. See also LLRP Specification Section 12.2.6 and LLRP Specification Section 16.2.6.6 .
